revision.text: [[Protein]] is a consumable item that you can purchase from shops of each region's League. It can be fed to a pokemon to increase the amount of damage it gain on each successful egg hatching when you breed it. Your pokemon gain 1 damage for every Protein fed to it. Each pokemon can consume 10 Protien at a time with addition 10 more for each new region you unlock.
